  <md:abstract><para>By the end of this section, you will be able to:</para>
<list>
<item>Define the magnetic field based on a moving charge experiencing a force</item>
<item>Apply the right-hand rule to determine the direction of a magnetic force based on the motion of a charge in a magnetic field</item>
<item>Sketch magnetic field lines to understand which way the magnetic field points and how strong it is in a region of space</item>
</list></md:abstract>
